import { Flex, VStack } from "@chakra-ui/react"

const Login = () => {
    return (
        <Flex>
            <VStack>
                <FormControl>
                    <FormLabel>Email address</FormLabel>
                    <Input type='email' />
                    <FormHelperText>We'll never share your email.</FormHelperText>
                    </FormControl>
            </VStack>
        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Login
